									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Speech act</b> is a technical term in <a href="/wiki/Linguistics" title="Linguistics">linguistics</a> and the <a href="/wiki/Philosophy_of_language" title="Philosophy of language">philosophy of language</a>. Precise conceptions vary.</p>
